1 WHEREAS, Kirby was a devoted husband to his wife, Tasha Dawson, with whom
2 he shared more than twenty-eight years of love, laughter, and partnership; he was a proud
3 father to Chris, Loghan, and Shawn, and his family was his most cherished gift in life; and
4 WHEREAS, Kirby Shawn Dawson was an inspiring community servant, and while
5 he will be deeply missed, his legacy of love shall live on in the hearts and minds of those
6 who were privileged to have known and loved him.
7 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
8 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby express heartfelt condolences on the death of Kirby
9 Shawn Dawson; does hereby offer enduring appreciation for his dedicated service and
10 community leadership throughout his law enforcement career; and does hereby extend
11 sincere wishes that his family, friends, colleagues, and loved ones find comfort in their
12 shared memories of his beautiful life.
